      "recording_attendee_id": "e39df327-5207-4d43-b7d1-2075cac45ea9",
      "order_number": 101,
      "text": "And then obviously like Lincoln, we have a call with them tomorrow to finalize basically the uh, the billing and the official unit count and all that."
